%% Diagram: Async error propagation
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Call as Caller
    participant AF as async fn
    participant P as Promise<br/>state machine
    participant MT as Microtask<br/>queue
    participant Top as Top-level<br/>handler

    Call->>AF: call (returns Promise)
    AF->>AF: await fetch(...)
    Note over AF: throw inside try?
    alt try / catch present
        AF->>AF: catch (e)
        AF-->>Call: resolved / rethrown
    else awaited but no try
        AF->>P: reject(reason)
        P->>MT: schedule reaction
        MT->>Call: throw at await site
    else Promise dropped (no await, no .catch)
        AF->>P: reject(reason)
        P->>MT: schedule HostPromiseRejectionTracker
        MT->>Top: 'unhandledrejection' / 'unhandledRejection'
        Note over Top: Node 15+: process exits<br/>Browser: console error
    end
